<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21624931">为什么大学里很世故的女生大部分想以后靠男人，而很单纯的女生都想靠自己？难道是我错了嘛？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="830704" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
